  "Description": {
    "English": "Partial coordinate data, acquired from a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">starship</span> crashed on an ocean bed. The chart is signed with a snippet of pirate manifesto:<br><br>\"Annihilate every Traveller! All galaxies will fall to Blight!\"<br><br>The navigational information is unreadable in its current state, but appears to be linked to the data acquired from the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">freighter captain</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "部分坐标数据，从一艘坠落在海床上的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船</span>上获得。图表上书写着一句海盗宣言：<br><br>“消灭所有的旅行者！所有的星系都将为瘟疫沦陷！”<br><br>导航信息在当前状态下无法阅读，但似乎与从<span class=\"name name-stellar\">货船船长</span>那里获得的数据有关。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "部分座標資料，從墜毀在海床的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船</span>上取得。該圖表上簽署了一段海盜宣言：<br><br>「殲滅所有的旅行者！所有銀河系都將落入『毀滅』的手裡！」<br><br>導航資訊目前的狀態無法讀取，但似乎和從<span class=\"name name-stellar\">貨船船長</span>身上取得的資料有所關聯。"
  },
